replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"之前係馬場屌到個司機反車單野<br />\n個司機點判？"},{"pid":"652e2b92373b593ca721b2ef21a0d2cea0d7e7b2","tid":2507654,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3025d36047a4f5f5342c80455d785fa8c31a763d","tid":2507654,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3a4b00284805ddbd3e893e2f917a9dc0872e724","tid":2507654,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15fda88e08bccb642c81c910dc22fca10789f71","tid":2507654,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"另一單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"個單判咗未？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"判左啦 坐十幾年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"咁都十幾年<br />\n班廢老抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e281b162679785ea81b85149f5d92f5b0224ed01","tid":2507654,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0fe21e5bc6fb2138a4e7a5d940aa1bb4b0074e9a","tid":2507654,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"之前係馬場屌到個司機反車單野<br />\n個司機點判？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"2020年7月7日，自小被診斷患有亞氏保加症的被告在高等法院承認19項誤殺罪及19項危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪，合共38項控罪。辯方律師求情指被告承認犯案時失控導致意外，但他當時只是不懂處理乘客反應，並非如乘客所想的在發脾氣，而公司在他學習駕駛872號線時沒有提供慣常培訓，僅用私家車載他跟路線，不熟悉路況亦是意外原因。法官李素蘭斥責被告自私，未理會乘客安全，明顯不會控制情緒，並讓其情緒影響駕駛判斷，用車輛作為報復他人的武器，判每項誤殺罪入獄14年、每項危險駕駛引致他人嚴重受傷罪入獄4年，所有刑期同期執行，合共判被告入獄14年，並終身停牌。法官亦特別將本案與南丫島海難比較，指本案被告蓄意以惡劣態度駕車，案情較後者更嚴重。"},{"pid":"1a527acd74983fd23c9dce619ab4362f1bb3ebb4","tid":2507654,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"南丫島咩船難連死亡證都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2737028cec0dce4d0321bac1651e817bf70499","tid":2507654,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1c1235cf4aca9e6332e0a8c65cf4b8e3de46009","tid":2507654,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"係咪廢老賭馬嘈住個司機嗰單？定係另一單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"粉嶺撞樹個單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa2aa469c6d5f2abe1881305355b7fef5af9698","tid":2507654,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a335ea904f026a3f98ec2d62bf09b858ba193fe","tid":2507654,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"呢單我反而無咩印象 一開頭仲以為係幾年前馬場加一班廢老個單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇多陣先發現唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"x2<br />\n馬場嗰單我記得個巴士司機有反社會人格"},{"pid":"4635a7665b84dcdec37b911dcaf493fe85a3a7d9","tid":2507654,"uid":202898,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"搵萬五俾八九千家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢老母死左個米飯班主<br />\n加個支拿未婚妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死左仲好"},{"pid":"6ada459370837e36c88b9a81d8834e93b0ba721d","tid":2507654,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得上層有個人d血流到好誇"},{"pid":"cbed38f637d8b0511ec6368c5f5ab9e4c7aacc7f","tid":2507654,"uid":202898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4635a7665b84dcdec37b911dcaf493fe85a3a7d9","tid":2507654,"uid":202898,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"搵萬五俾八九千家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"